Antica Osteria

via Venezia 11, Ossana, 38026, Italy
€€ · Regional Cuisine, Seasonal Cuisine
Bib Gourmand: good quality, good value cooking
A pleasant restaurant with three charming dining rooms, where the whole family pulls together with spectacular results. Delicious regional cuisine is to the fore, with dishes such as venison carpaccio with pineapple and raspberries on the menu.
